campaign includes a large format sign dis
played outside of NEC's concert hall, a program
stuffer inserted into concert programs at all of
NEC's concerts for the month of December, an
email graphic, and a web graphic for NEC's
website. After designing multiple concepts for
this campaign, I decided on the sweater design
because it felt the most attention grabbing,
holiday-neutral, and relevant to today's holiday
fads. A giant sweater on Huntington Ave felt
sure to grab the attention of everyone walking
by, and attract potential audience members to
